    @GwtIncompatible
public final class MutableClassToInstanceMap<B extends @Nullable java.lang.Object>
extends ForwardingMap<java.lang.Class<? extends @NonNull B>,​B>
implements ClassToInstanceMap<B>, java.io.Serializable
    A mutable class-to-instance map backed by an arbitrary user-provided map. See also ImmutableClassToInstanceMap.

    See the Guava User Guide article on ClassToInstanceMap.

    Since:
    2.0
